<br/></li></ul></div><h2 id='LaeACAhdfLa'>How?</h2>

<p id='LaeACATtMX2' class='line'>Essentially:</p>

<div data-section-style='6'><ul id='LaeACANUihw'><li id='LaeACAAJ7GU' class='' value='1'><span id='LaeACAAJ7GU'>Build a multidisciplinary team and provide them with all of the resources needed to rapidly prototype and manufacture hardware, software, webware, and service-based solutions for the emergent "internet of things,” as well as traditional computing devices.  </span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACADrgqP' class=''><span id='LaeACADrgqP'>Develop and <b>commercialize</b> open hardware products that span every price bracket using modular components.</span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACAlKz0U' class=''><span id='LaeACAlKz0U'>Develop open software with clear applications in today's world.</span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACA2Defn' class=''><span id='LaeACA2Defn'>Run a firmware repository containing firmware for both open and opened technology platforms.</span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACAD95Cp' class='parent'><span id='LaeACAD95Cp'>Leverage our 100% transparent, open business model to enhance:</span>

<br/></li><ul><li id='LaeACA2DAfO' class=''><span id='LaeACA2DAfO'>recruiting</span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACACBjSD' class=''><span id='LaeACACBjSD'>customers and suppliers understanding of our strategies</span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACAuetMY' class=''><span id='LaeACAuetMY'>public awareness of our solutions</span>

<br/></li></ul><li id='LaeACAlYtB6' class=''><span id='LaeACAlYtB6'>In order to have an excellent product pipeline and top talent, support open technology projects of every type.</span>

<br/></li><li id='LaeACAXeZ8W' class=''><span id='LaeACAXeZ8W'>Intentionally integrate our projects and corporate ownership as appropriate, while seeking further integration opportunities.  </span>

<br/></li></ul></div>